I want to use a bunch of free tiers on various osint platforms to automate osint workflows and probs integrate into my other projects

intelx curl
curl -H "X-API-Key: YOUR_API_KEY" "https://api.intelligencex.example/email?address=user@example.com" 

shodan curl
curl -sS "https://api.shodan.io/shodan/host/8.8.8.8?key=YOUR_SHODAN_API_KEY"

hunter curl
curl -sS "https://api.hunter.io/v2/domain-search?domain=example.com&api_key=YOUR_HUNTER_API_KEY"
